'Updating' – the Cosmos DB account is being updated. 'Deleting' – the Cosmos DB account is being deleted. 'Failed' – the Cosmos DB account failed creation. 'Offline' - the Cosmos DB account is not active. 'DeletionFailed' – the Cosmos DB account deletion failed.

'Updating' – the Cosmos DB account is being updated. 'Deleting' – the Cosmos DB account is being deleted. 'Failed' – the Cosmos DB account failed creation. 'DeletionFailed' – the Cosmos DB account deletion failed.
